        GUIDE_WITH_PARTNER_LINK_DESC:"<p className='mb-0'><strong>Where do I get their profile link?</strong></p><p>You'll need to ask them for the link, which they can get at the bottom of their profile.</p><img src={0} alt=''/><p>If they haven't taken the test, they will need to do so before you can read the guide with them. We need their personality to generate the guide.</p><p><strong>If you don't have their profile link right now, you can come back to this page at any time.</strong> On the Relationship Guides homepage, you'll see a button to Select who you want the guide with.</p><img src={1} alt=''/>",
