        //Guide Home
        GUIDE_HOME_PRIVACY_CONSENT_DESC: "<p>Interpersonality is all about improving your relationships - with friends, family, at work, and romantically.</p><p>In this part of the website, we help you improve your romantic relationships, using the insights of our personality model combined with 40 years of research.</p><p>In the process, we may receive information that we could use to infer your sexual orientation. That is because we use the personality of you and another person to give our advice, and we know both of your genders. GDPR privacy laws require we get your explicit consent to process this information for the purpose explained above. In order for you to use this part of the site and improve your relationships, we need your consent. For more info see the <a href=\"/privacy\"><b>Privacy Policy</b></a>.</p><p>I give my consent to process my information:</p>",
        GUIDE_HOME_PRIVACY_CONSENT_UPDATE_BTN: "YES, I GIVE MY CONSENT",
        GUIDE_HOME_PRIVACY_CONSENT_NOT_NOW_BTN: "<b>Not right now</b>",
        GUIDE_HOME_TITLE:"<p className=\"sub-heading\">PREMIUM</p><h2>Relationship Guides</h2><p>Nothing affects your happiness like romantic relationships. Don't leave it to chance.</p>",
        GUIDE_HOME_ROMENTIC_TITLE: "<h3>Romantic Compatibility <span>{0}{1}</span></h3>",
        GUIDE_HOME_COUPLE_TITLE: "<h3>For Couples <span>{0}{1}</span></h3>",
        GUIDE_HOME_ROMANTIC_DESC: "<p>Find out how compatible you are with someone. We'll let you know exactly what problems you'd have in a long-term relationship with them, and help you understand how they approach dating.</p>",
        GUIDE_HOME_COUPLE_DESC: "<p>If you're trying to fix your relationship, there's a good chance you're actually making things worse. What will fix one relationship will destroy another. We'll tell you what the real problems are in your relationship - and how to fix things before it's too late.</p>",
        GUIDE_HOME_LEARN_BTN: "Learn more",
